{"version":1,"entries":{"tv_240441_keywords":{"at":1772469927739,"data":{"id":240441,"results":[{"name":"1920s","id":207876},{"name":"chinese republican era","id":286630}]}},"person_2633279_translations":{"at":1772469929665,"data":{"id":2633279,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"He is a film and television actor, pop singer, and program host in Mainland China. He graduated from the Department of Culture Communication of Jining College. In 2018, he appeared in his first film and television drama \"Waiting for you in the future\", thus officially entering the entertainment circle; in August, as an intern teacher participated in the iQiyi parent-child experimental reality show \"Super Kindergarten\"; September 17th, launched the first A solo single \"Wish\". In 2019, as a regular guest, participated in the iQiyi RV Touring Reality Show \"The Flower Road of Youth\";  in May, hosted the Zhejiang Satellite TV star Food Passing Emotional Reality Show \"Familiar Taste Season 4\". On April 24, 2021, the youth science fiction drama \"Orphan on Mars\" starring Fei Qiming was launched.","name":"Fei Qiming","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"费启鸣，中国影视男演员、流行乐歌手、节目主持人，毕业于济宁学院文化传播系。\n\n2018年，出演个人首部影视剧《我在未来等你》，从而正式进入演艺圈；8月，作为实习老师参加爱奇艺亲子实验真人秀节目《超能幼稚园》；9月17日，推出首支个人单曲《Wish》。2019年，作为固定嘉宾参加爱奇艺房车游历真人秀节目《青春的花路》；5月，主持浙江卫视明星美食传情感恩真人秀节目《熟悉的味道第四季》。","name":"费启鸣","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"費啟鳴","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Фэй Ци Мин","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"VN","iso_639_1":"vi","name":"Tiếng Việt","english_name":"Vietnamese","data":{"biography":"","name":"Phí Khải Minh","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말"